			 	<li class="l_badge" style="display:block;">
			 		<div class="p_badge">
			 			<a href="/f/like/level?kw=%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6&ie=utf-8&lv_t=lv_nav_intro" target="_blank" class="user_badge d_badge_bright d_badge_icon1" title="本吧头衔1级，经验值0，点击进入等级头衔说明页"><div class="d_badge_title ">寒窗多年</div><div class="d_badge_lv">1</div></a>
